IMAPStore maximbaz-remote
Host mail.maximbaz.com
User me@maximbaz.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.cache/mail.maximbaz.com"
SSLType IMAPS

MaildirStore maximbaz-local
Path ~/.mail/maximbaz/
Inbox ~/.mail/maximbaz/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel maximbaz
Master :maximbaz-remote:
Slave :maximbaz-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *
